cargo-declare-parenttable-bad-parameter: Nuṣiwa: "$1" e ma yin nue yin alọkẹyi.
cargo-declare-parenttable-not-exist: Nuṣiwa: Nue din a te "$1" ehe ma tin.
cargo-declare-validate-has-whitespace: Nuṣiwa: $1 yinkọ "$2" lọ gọna nue ma yin alọkẹyi. Nue ma yin alọkẹyi depope ma dona yin yiyizan; a sọgan gbọ bo zan owhì odò tọn ehe ("_").
cargo-declare-validate-starts-underscore: Nuṣiwa: $1 yinkọ "$2" lọ bẹjẹeji po owhì odò tọn po; ehe ma yin alọkẹyi.
cargo-declare-validate-ends-underscore: Nuṣiwa: $1 yinkọ "$2" lọ tindo owhì odò tọn to vivọnu ; ehe ma yin alọkẹyi.
cargo-declare-validate-gt1-underscore: Nuṣiwa: $1 yinkọ "$2" lọ gọ̀ na owhì odò tọn he hugan awè to ofi dopolọ; ehe ma yin alọkẹyi.
cargo-declare-validate-bad-character: Nuṣiwa: depope to wekun ehelẹ mẹ ma dona sọawuhia to $1 yinkọ "$2" mẹ: $3
